Invocation Name: carlock
Developer Terms of Use
des: CarLock is now integrated with Alexa and can help you locate your car at any time. It also enables CarLock monitoring system without you having to use your phone at all! This skill requires the CarLock device, which can be purchased on http://amzn.com/B00U0K3Q10 and valid CarLock account.
